教育課程表（授業科目一覧等）は、下記リンクこちらに掲載していますので学修計画の参考にしてください。\nhttps://kwic.kwansei.ac.jp/cabinet/reference?typeCd=0&amp;cabinetId=557&amp;directLink=1\n※kwicへのリンクとなります（在学生のみ閲覧可）"], "成績評価Grading0": ["種別　Type備考　Note", "割合　Percentage", "評価基準等　Grading Criteria etc."], "成績評価Grading1": ["その他／Others (99)", "100 %", "Class participation 20% Assignment 10% Vocab Quizzes 10% Tests 60%"], "成績評価Grading2": ["備考　Note Class Participation 20%Assignment          10%Vocabulary Quizzes  10%Tests               60%Total              100%Any online students will be given assignments instead of tests; the assignments will be worth 60% of the final grade."], "備考Note0": ["https://sites.google.com/view/vocabularyseiwa/\nStudents who are absent on assignment day will be given another chance, possibly on a Saturday morning. \nInstructor's email address: aot06033@kwansei.ac.jp"], "備考Note1": ["2022-Paul's Rules and Requests.docx", ""], "備考Note2": ["2026年01月25日 11時23分28秒"], "項番No.0": [], "項番No.1": ["2026年度", "春学期／Spring", "金曜４時限／Friday 4", "春学期／Spring", "３３３教室"]}, "campas": 4, "name": "【210】英語ＢIII　９／English BIII", "管理部署": 9, "単位数": 1, "担当者": "アロエ　ポール（AALOE PAUL） ", "履修基準年度": "２年", "履修登録方法": "予備登録", "開講期": 1, "時限1": 31, "評価1": 6, "成績評価備考": "備考　Note\nClass Participation 20%\nAssignment 10%\nVocabulary Quizzes 10%\nTests 60%\nTotal 100%\nAny online students will be given assignments instead of tests; the assignments will be worth 60% of the final grade."}